{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require child friendly hand washing facilities in public and business toilets",
        "additional_details": "Parents often have to try and lift their children up and wash their hands at the same time when at a public or business toilet, resulting them squashing them or nearly dropping them. Some have lower sinks for children but most don\u2019t.",
        "background": "Make it mandatory for public and business-owned toilets to have accessible hand washing facilities for children. A simple step would suffice.\r\n",
